---
layout: base.njk
title: Playbooks
description: Deep-dive methodologies, free forever. Proof of Work Sourcing, AI tool scorecards, Boolean-to-AI transition, n8n workflows.
permalink: /playbooks/
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---

<section class="library-hero">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <div class="eyebrow">Playbook Library</div>
    <h1 class="library-title">Deep dives. Free. Forever.</h1>
    <p class="library-dek">
      Full methodologies. Step-by-step. Screenshots, prompts, scripts, decision trees.
      Built from 18 months of testing across 28 client briefs. Everything public,
      no signup required.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="library-list">
  <div class="container">
    {% set playbooks = collections.playbook | reverse %}
    {% if playbooks.length > 0 %}
      <div class="playbook-grid">
        {% for post in playbooks %}
        <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="playbook-card">
          <div class="playbook-status {{ post.data.status | lower }}">
            {{ post.data.status or 'Available' }}
          </div>
          <h2 class="playbook-title">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
          {% if post.data.dek %}<p class="playbook-desc">{{ post.data.dek }}</p>{% endif %}
          <div class="playbook-meta">
            {% if post.data.readingTime %}<span class="playbook-length">{{ post.data.readingTime }} read</span>{% endif %}
            <span class="playbook-arrow">Read →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    {% else %}
      <div class="empty-state">
        <div class="empty-eyebrow">Coming soon</div>
        <p>Four playbooks are in development for 2026. Follow <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/sourcing-strategist/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Brendan on LinkedIn</a> for release announcements, or subscribe to the <a href="/newsletters/">Wednesday briefing</a>.</p>
      </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.library-hero {
  padding: var(--s-8) 0 var(--s-5);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
}

.library-title {
  font-family: var(--f-display);
  font-weight: 900;
  font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 64px);
  line-height: 0.98;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  color: var(--parch);
  margin-bottom: var(--s-3);
}

.library-dek {
  font-size: 18px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: var(--slate);
  max-width: 580px;
}

.library-list { padding: var(--s-5) 0 var(--s-7); }

.playbook-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  gap: var(--s-3);
}

.playbook-card {
  background: var(--navy);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
  border-radius: var(--r-card);
  padding: var(--s-5);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--s-3);
  text-decoration: none;
  color: inherit;
  transition: border-color 180ms ease, transform 180ms ease;
}

.playbook-card:hover {
  border-color: var(--border-strong);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

.playbook-card:hover .playbook-title { color: var(--gold); }
.playbook-card:hover .playbook-arrow { color: var(--gold); }

.playbook-status {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  font-family: var(--f-mono);
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 500;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.16em;
  color: var(--gold4);
  padding: 3px 10px;
  border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
  border-radius: 99px;
  align-self: flex-start;
  background: rgba(255, 195, 0, .04);
}

.playbook-status.available,
.playbook-status.live {
  color: var(--green);
  border-color: rgba(34, 197, 94, .3);
  background: rgba(34, 197, 94, .06);
}

.playbook-title {
  font-family: var(--f-display);
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 22px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.015em;
  color: var(--parch);
  line-height: 1.15;
  transition: color 180ms ease;
}

.playbook-desc {
  font-size: 14.5px;
  color: var(--slate);
  line-height: 1.6;
  flex: 1;
}

.playbook-meta {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  padding-top: var(--s-3);
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
}

.playbook-length {
  font-family: var(--f-mono);
  font-size: 10px;
  color: var(--slate);
  letter-spacing: 0.14em;
}

.playbook-arrow {
  font-family: var(--f-mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--gold4);
  letter-spacing: 0.14em;
  transition: color 180ms ease;
}

.empty-state {
  text-align: center;
  padding: var(--s-7) var(--s-4);
  background: var(--navy);
  border: 1px dashed var(--border-med);
  border-radius: var(--r-card);
  max-width: 580px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.empty-eyebrow {
  font-family: var(--f-mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 500;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  color: var(--gold);
  margin-bottom: var(--s-3);
}

.empty-state p {
  font-size: 16px;
  color: var(--slate);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.empty-state a {
  color: var(--gold);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 195, 0, .3);
  text-decoration: none;
}

@media (max-width: 720px) {
  .playbook-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
</style>
